-- Ambac rescue could be announced Mon or Tues: report
-- 
-- Fri Feb 22, 2008 4:17pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/02/22/us-ambac-bailout-idUSWEN406620080222

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Banks rescuing Ambac Financial Group Inc ABK.N could announce a plan as soon as Monday or Tuesday, CNBC's Charles Gasparino said on Friday. 

 The details of the deal are still being worked out and the plan may fall through, Gasparino said. Ambac shares rose after the report, trading at $9.90, up 7.3 percent, in trading on Friday afternoon. (Reporting by  Dan Wilchins ; Editing by  Andre Grenon )